    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this breathtaking specimen, presented in what can only be described as showroom-fresh condition. The deep metallic paint retains its original factory luster, free from any swirls, chips, or imperfections, having been professionally ceramic coated and climate-control garaged since day one. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and that distinct 'new car' scent still lingers. Every button, switch, and digital interface functions with crisp, tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians\u2014full service records are meticulously organized and ready for your review. This vehicle has never seen rain, let alone a winter road, and sits on flawless alloy wheels wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber. Complete with both original keys, all owner manuals, and custom-fit floor mats, this is the definitive choice for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than a flawless driving experience.",
      "price": 46500.0,
